<br />
no cumulative rule so play 3 of these...and they all count.<br />
<br />
this is strictly a limited card, and might even be a good limited card depending on how often you expect someone to be right at 4 tactics. in swccg people would routinely sit right at 4 tactics - this could stop their draw - and essentially causes 2 more casualties if you win (1 less power - 1 less defense). that effect can be huge - you clear a site and don't lose anything to attrition.<br />
<br />
i doubt this is playable at all in constructed - unless a card was made that at tactics = 0 characters are destroyed.<br />
